<subSubSection pageId="9" pageNumber="326" type="distribution">
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6639384" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6639384" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6639384/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="326" targetBox="[1435,2026,2077,2490]" targetPageId="9">
<paragraph blockId="9.[2049,2644,2070,2496]" pageId="9" pageNumber="326">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[2050,2226,2306,2339]" pageId="9" pageNumber="326">Distribution.</emphasis>
Known from three counties (Tengchong, Longling, and Longyang) of Baoshan in the Gaoligong National Nature Reserve, Yunnan, S China.
</paragraph>
</caption>
